---
import Head from '../../../../components/Head.astro';
import Footer from '../../../../components/Footer.astro';
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <Head title="Privacy Policy (AutoBooks)"/>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main>
      <h1>Privacy Policy (<span class="accent">AutoBooks</span>)</h1>
      <a href="/apps/autobooks">Go back</a>
      
      <p>AutoBooks itself does not collect, store, or share any personal information or data from its users.</p>
      <p>The app does use the OpenAI API, and forwards information about the books created to OpenAI in order to generate them.</p>
      <p>For more information on what OpenAI collects through their API, please read their privacy policy.</p>
      <p>By using AutoBooks, you acknowledge that OpenAI may collect and process information about the books you generate, and that AutoBooks itself does not collect any user data.</p>

    </main>

    <Footer />
    <script src="https://pagering.gideon.sh/embed.js" defer></script>
  </body>
</html>